patthana14.33:1.1: Pariyāpannaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca naapariyāpanno dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana14.33:2.1: Apariyāpannaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca naapariyāpanno dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Apariyāpannaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca napariyāpanno dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Apariyāpannaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca napariyāpanno ca naapariyāpanno ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā.
patthana14.33:3.1: Pariyāpannañca apariyāpannañca dhammaṁ paṭicca naapariyāpanno dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.  (Saṅkhittaṁ.)
patthana14.33:4.1: Hetuyā pañca, ārammaṇe dve …pe… avigate pañca.
